#: landing/templates/about.html:37 landing/templates/about1.html:28
msgid "about-0"
msgstr "Hello! My name is Artur"

#: landing/templates/about.html:39 landing/templates/about1.html:31
msgid "about-1"
msgstr ""
"Originally from Rio de Janeiro, Brazil, I am someone who has traveled "
"internationally from a very early age. I have lived in six different "
"countries, experiencing great culture and cuisine, but also repression and "
"authoritarianism."

#: landing/templates/about.html:40 landing/templates/about1.html:32
msgid "about-2"
msgstr "It was a bit much for such a young mind, to be honest."

#: landing/templates/about.html:41 landing/templates/about1.html:33
msgid "about-3"
msgstr ""
"I even studied Political Science in the USA and Law in Brazil to make sense "
"of it all — spoiler alert: it didn’t help."

#: landing/templates/about.html:42 landing/templates/about1.html:34
msgid "about-4"
msgstr ""
"But I found purpose in my marriage, and my mind still refuses to quiet down "
"about the world around me."

#: landing/templates/about.html:43 landing/templates/about1.html:35
msgid "about-5"
msgstr ""
"I moved to Porto with my wife in search of a better quality of life, and the "
"city has engulfed my very being. Although I have distant family connections "
"to Porto, nothing prepared me for how profoundly historical and storied it "
"is."

#: landing/templates/about.html:44 landing/templates/about1.html:36
msgid "about-6"
msgstr ""
"Becoming a tour guide was a natural extension of all the research I was "
"already doing to satisfy my own curiosity. Yet it has taken on a life of its "
"own. I fell in love with guiding and hope to carry this work for the rest of "
"my life."

#: landing/templates/about.html:45 landing/templates/about1.html:37
msgid "about-7"
msgstr ""
"Artuarium, the temple of my mind, exists so I can have conversations and "
"share information outside the tour format. I have many plans and my whole "
"life ahead of me — a life dedicated to my family, my studies, and dialogue."

#: landing/templates/about.html:46 landing/templates/about1.html:38
msgid "about-8"
msgstr ""
"If you are here, I hope it is because you are interested in my journey."

#: landing/templates/about.html:47 landing/templates/about1.html:39
msgid "about-9"
msgstr "It is a pleasure to have you alongside me."

#: landing/templates/about.html:48 landing/templates/about1.html:40
msgid "about-10"
msgstr ""
"If you’d like to support me on my journey, click below to find out more"

